Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你是要将这机体送往哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰达斯境内 本公司的服务中心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈兹福特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯贝尔尼斯工业公司的技师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯贝尔尼斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这么个制造商吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本公司是新锐企业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持有银色歼灭者技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为业界瞩目的快速成长股
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是关注度持续升温的企业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那机体 是叫银色{\rsymbol}…{\r}歼灭者{\rsymbol}…{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者{\rsymbol}…{\r}稳定型原型机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新锐的{\rsymbol}…{\r}U-link系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可将内载驾驶员的思维模式 转入曳战者的控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使性能上{\rsymbol}…{\r}有望获得飞跃性提升
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此系统的采用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼{\rsymbol}…{\r}歼灭者比以往的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天黑之前尽量拉开距离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带上那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,705)\fad(1000,1000))}觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗 走路麻利点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当这路线变更是谁害的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我害的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些反胃{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我吞回去坚持到下一个地点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他俩关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只能向本该绕开的敌人腹地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不{\rsymbol}…{\r}不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少你不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是放心这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看样子 是运输曳战者途中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试图将其截获 结果反被干掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻报告大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动流程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次换个模式试试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读入识别编号的同时 清除存储器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后动力部紧急启动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 或许能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力部接入传动系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陀螺仪稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,固定支撑脚后向前迈步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把时宗拽下来之后就一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试过所有模式 全行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是第一次遇到战争知识不适用的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-link系统转写的是最初一名操纵者的思维模式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男孩可以说已经成了启动钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要讲几遍你们才懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军人是经验主义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机师 进时宗上等兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他呀{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是初次上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次总难免如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姐不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让进时宗上等兵去驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人恐怕就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然成了钥匙 就要尽到钥匙的本分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是全部投降的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投降者还会继续增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我军必定会大举反击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 带下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备做得怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受扫讨作战的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后续部队抵达时间会稍有延误
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但能勉强赶上作战时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传令务必赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进攻作战的最终目标直捣敌人王都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果曳战者不能有效展开 作战会失去意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报告一下那场莫名的战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打击?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是说有过格斗战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并非枪械或刀剑之类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰达斯的曳战者应该没有这类性能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实他们只有些过时的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,残骸中 除一部阿兰达斯机体外 全为我军机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但查不到所属 很有可能是伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵也查不到所属
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的伪装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者说{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何处理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台新型曳战者的去向让人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续追踪调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情报部的人可能与此有关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面我会想办法应付
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扫讨作战中的部队那边 我这就去联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点注意姿势控制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重心移动不要依靠脚跟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比之前还差了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按你说的做才变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥当时动得那么顺畅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能搞清楚{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在读那个说明书似的玩意罢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是技师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有我就没有银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么动不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是划时代的新系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在那时{\rsymbol}…{\r}是第一次参战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只顾拼命根本什么都不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但下一次{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我到底哪里不对 你倒是看清点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于进行着金属精炼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这矿山除采掘隧道之外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有很大的烟道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能走这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席加 你先去探探
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快能清理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 敌人也不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真正棘手的是来回逃窜的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棘手?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不该很好对付的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白逃跑意义的人 必定存于败退之军中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要抹杀这些未来的强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废弃矿山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garm-1 已向那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军粮 终于咽得下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,状态如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很用功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点大家都认可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲虽然还很苛刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但银色歼灭者只有你能驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快记起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快记起来 吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对学过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这样的洞窟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是洞窟 是烟道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟道(远藤)先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是排烟的通路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭上嘴快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 新来的 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是去操纵{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对{\rsymbol}…{\r}对不起 我自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把载具扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-2 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不到人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我翻过山去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 请继续监视
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了 共三部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗机掉队了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这要爬山还有点难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-2 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到疑似逃跑路径了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进上等兵 收到请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人顺烟道追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就结果而言 你现在是殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫<殿后> 军校里学过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓<殿后>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是阻止敌人追击 掩护友军撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令 挡住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把敌人挡在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾久井上等兵带吉米小姐尽快与大部队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个叫时宗的怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为掩护你们与敌人交战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危险 你们尽快离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扔下不管?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前脚刚接收 后脚就要抛弃银色歼灭者?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过分 太自作主张了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者只有进上等兵才能驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是关乎部队存亡的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是说得什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把一个新兵留下自己逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服从命令是士兵的天职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平民给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但再怎么说这命令也太没天理了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当初不也无视命令救了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这才是最佳选择
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾久井 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我说得不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要想着怎么操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下 你现在想做什么 怎样做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不为获胜 也不为被人认同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 老实跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别随便瞎跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请放下我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟银色歼灭者{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令 要我带你安全归队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来不对啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是队长说的新型机?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟训练时学的技法不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接拳打脚踢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方只有一部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹击他 掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不战斗就会被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不能死在这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 G-3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈～身手不减当年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样 帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下身后追兵暂时能拖一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但前面不知道有多少敌人等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铃城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小姑娘 你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您指吉米小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他俩搭档不错啊 她和时宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈兹福特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫吉米就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那{\rsymbol}…{\r}吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我是50对50
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 打算如何处理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,500)\bord3\be1\fs60\fad(500,0)}一骑当千
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:34.98,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}この高き無望の空でいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:39.60,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}その意思は膝を立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:48.36,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.87,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:55.68,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… あの火は仲間か?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:00.43,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:05.92,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:09.80,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:15.61,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:20.75,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:26.00,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:30.57,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:31.82,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(640,660)}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:36.20,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:42.83,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.38,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…かかって来い{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:52.14,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.88,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.64,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.80,0:01:34.98,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}总有一天 向着这无望的高空
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.98,0:01:39.60,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志将一飞冲天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.87,0:01:55.68,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是战友吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.94,0:02:00.43,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}当走之路是黑暗吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.03,0:02:05.92,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 在面前寒光闪动
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.07,0:02:09.80,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无名感情在胸中翻涌
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.99,0:02:15.61,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-此时此刻在此地 尚不能结束-
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.61,0:02:20.75,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那么就做好活下去的准备吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.87,0:02:26.00,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一腔热忱 越积越高无处释放
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.00,0:02:30.57,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这份量 怎可能不沉重{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.95,0:02:36.20,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}战场之上 笑谈青涩有何不可
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.20,0:02:42.83,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我会一个一个亲自去实践
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.38,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…放马过来{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
